    "title": "Yuda Iskariote",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "yuda iskariote",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Yuda Iskarioti anajulikana sana kwa kumsaliti Yesu kwa viongozi wa mamlaka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:4\">Mathayo 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:19\">Marko 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:16\">Luka 6:16</a>).</p><p>Maana ya jina &quot;Iskariote&quot; haifahamiki vizuri. Inaweza kumaanisha kijiji kinachoitwa Keriothi. Yuda Iskarioti ni tofauti na Yuda, mwana wa Yakobo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:16\">Luka 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:22\">Yohana 14:22</a>).</p><p>Miongoni mwa mitume (wafuasi wa karibu wa Yesu), Yuda Iskarioti alijulikana kama mlafi. Alikuwa akibeba mfuko wa pesa na alikuwa na sifa ya kuiba kutoka humo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:4-John12:6\">Yohana 12:4–6</a>). Makuhani wakuu baadaye walimpa hongo, ambayo ilimshawishi kumsaliti Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:16\">Mathayo 26:14–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:10-Mark14:11\">Marko 14:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:3-Luke22:6\">Luka 22:3–6</a>).</p><p>Yesu alimwita Yuda &quot;shetani&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:70-John6:71\">Yohana 6:70–71</a>). Pia alitabiri usaliti wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:18-Mark14:21\">Marko 14:18–21</a>). Shetani aliweka wazo la usaliti katika akili ya Yuda, na Shetani akaingia ndani yake wakati wa usaliti (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:3-Luke22:4\">Luka 22:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:2\">Yohana 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:27\">27</a>). Yuda aliwaongoza askari na maafisa kwenye bustani ya Gethsemane usiku. Huko, alimkuta Yesu na wafuasi wake. Yuda alikuwa amepanga kumtambua Yesu kwa askari kwa kumpa busu, ambayo ilikuwa njia ya kawaida ya kumsalimu mtu wakati huo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:43-Mark14:46\">Marko 14:43–46</a>). Baadaye, Yuda alijuta sana kwa kumsaliti mtu asiye na hatia. Alijiua kwa kujinyonga (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:10\">Mathayo 27:3–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:18-Acts1:19\">Matendo 1:18–19</a>).</p><p>Yesu alielewa usaliti wa Yuda kama sehemu ya mpango wa Mungu wa ukombozi. Ulipelekea kifo cha Yesu, Masihi, kama dhabihu kuu kwa ajili ya dhambi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">Mathayo 26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:53-Matt26:54\">53–54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:21\">Marko 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:22\">Luka 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:12\">Yohana 17:12</a>). Ingawa Yuda alihusika katika mpango wa Mungu, mwisho wake wa kusikitisha ulikuwa unastahili (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:24-Acts1:25\">Matendo 1:24–25</a>). Ingekuwa bora kwa Yuda kama asingezaliwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">Mathayo 26:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:21\">Marko 14:21</a>). Hatima ya Yuda inatumika kama onyo kwa wale wanaoonekana kumfuata Yesu lakini hawajajitolea binafsi kwake (angalia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:6\">Waebrania 6:4–6</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:4\">Mathayo 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:16\">26:14–16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:23-Matt26:25\">23–25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:46-Matt26:50\">46–50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:10\">27:3–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:19\">Marko 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:10-Mark14:11\">14:10–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:18-Mark14:21\">18–21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:43-Mark14:45\">43–45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:16\">Luka 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:3-Luke22:6\">22:3–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:22\">22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:47-Luke22:48\">47–48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:70-John6:71\">Yohana 6:70–71</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:4-John12:6\">12:4–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:2\">13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:18\">18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:21-John13:30\">21–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:12\">17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:2-John18:5\">18:2–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:16-Acts1:26\">Matendo 1:16–26</a></p>",
